<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thermo Comfort - Home</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/HomePage.css">

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</head>
<div class="text-center">
    <h1 style="font-family:'Merriweather';color:darkgreen"> Добре дошли в ТермоКомфорт</h1>

</div>

<body>

    <div id="carouselExample" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
   
        <div class="carousel-indicators">
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExample" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExample" data-bs-slide-to="1"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExample" data-bs-slide-to="2"></button>
        </div>

        <!-- Слайдър за снимки -->
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active" data-bs-interval="3000">
                <img src="~/Images/cozyInteriorSlider.webp" class="d-block w-100" alt="Slide 1">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <p>Най-иновативните технологии на пазара! </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item active" data-bs-interval="3000">
                <img src="~/Images/gasBoilerSlider.webp" class="d-block w-100" alt="Slide 2">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <p>Най-новите модели!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item active" data-bs-interval="3000">
                <img src="~/Images/pelletStoveSlider.webp" class="d-block w-100" alt="Slide 3">
                <div class="carousel-caption" >
                    <p>Най-добри и конкурентни цени!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Стрелките на слайдъра -->
        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExample" data-bs-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExample" data-bs-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon"></span>
        </button>
    </div>
    <section class="features">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Защо да изберете ТермоКомфорт?</h2>
            <div class="feature-grid">
                <div class="feature">
                    <h3>С мисъл за природата</h3>
                    <p>Нашите продукти са с ниска консумация на енергия, за да опазим околната среда.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <h3>Високо качество</h3>
                    <p>Ние предлагаме най-добрите решения за отопление с първокласно качество.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <h3>Обслужване на клиенти</h3>
                    <p>Обслужване от 8:00 - 18:00ч., за да ви помогнем с всичките ви нужди от отопление.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

  
</body>
</html>